      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG CASH (3) ran below best last time finishing fourth (22.78) over 388m at this track in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Ready to return to form. SILVER CHAIN (2) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing six from 11 starts. Finished in the money last time though when third (23.44) at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in three starts. Will give a great sight again. KUNDA (4) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.77) at Maitland behind Road To Fame in a Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Expected to feature. HELLO PRETZEL (5) can run a bold race on best form.",
